item.title: Business
item.description: Meet Imaculate the business-woman. You are probably wondering, how did we get here? Did I quit my tech job? What happened to the running-inspired articles? Thanks for asking; No I’m still a Software Engineer who runs a lot. I just added another line to my resume. If you stick around, you’ll find out that this venture was very much inspired by running. You are probably why? The answer lies somewhere in curiosity, fun and obsession.
